Package org.dspace.statistics.export.dao

Interface OpenURLTrackerDAO

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GenericDAO<OpenURLTracker>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OpenURLTrackerDAOImpl
    public interface OpenURLTrackerDAO
extends GenericDAO<OpenURLTracker>
    Database Access Object interface class for the OpenURLTracker object. The implementation of this class is responsible for all database calls for the OpenURLTracker object and is autowired by spring This class should only be accessed from a single service and should never be exposed outside of the API

      • Methods inherited from interface org.dspace.core.GenericDAO

        create, delete, findAll, findAll, findByID, findByID, findMany, findUnique, save
